\section{The Hello World Problem}


In this project I am attempting to solve the well-know hello world problem. In
this problem we tried to make the computer display  {\bf hello World} on the
screen using the Object oriented programming language, Java. Although there have
been many solutions in other languages including
Mandarin~\cite{KuhnScottAndreev2008}, we believe this is the first solution to
the problem in Welsh.



